      "rationale": "Testing was performed at a single load configuration (ASTM F1717 standard setup, 10 mm offset). No variation in load level, offset distance, or rod diameter was explored. The achieved gradation (2) falls short of the required gradation (3) for this model risk level. This gap is acknowledged; the assessment team notes that the single-condition dataset is sufficient for the specific regulatory submission scope, and that the acceptance criterion for the primary QoIs (E/uval < 1.96) is met across all 11 constructs."
